{"TopicId":99535,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.1.3] FlagRotate - Adjust flag orientation","CreatedByName":"xEvilReeperx","CreatedById":75857,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-13T03:56:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"xEvilReeperx","CreatedById":75857,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-13T03:56:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is an update to an older addon I made some time ago to fix a small but annoying problem, especially if you like to take screenshots of your accomplishments. For some reason those darned flags like to come out at just the wrong angle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/a/CC8aS\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EJavascript is disabled. View full album\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith this addon, you\u0027ll be able to spin your flag around on its pole while in EVA to face whichever way you\u0027d like. Changes are persistent. Applies to all flags. Angle and button names adjustable in the config.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://bitbucket.org/xEvilReeperx/ksp_flagrotate/downloads/KSP-1.1.3-FlagRotate.zip\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDownload\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://bitbucket.org/xEvilReeperx/ksp_flagrotate\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESource\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLicense: MIT\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-07T11:59:07Z\u0022 title=\u002207/07/2016 11:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 7, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by xEvilReeperx\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E1.1.3\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-13T03:57:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou\u0027ve fixed the \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003EChameleon\u003C/span\u003ERotational Circuit.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-13T05:33:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBrilliant! The second best solution to this problem there is (the first being not having the problem in the first place).\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NikoKun","CreatedById":136647,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-13T14:25:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAwesome! I didn\u0027t even know I needed this, but I was always annoyed that the Kerbals tend to turn and face random directions when planting flags. lol\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is almost something that should be part of TweakableEverything. heh Brilliant!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Finnan","CreatedById":130706,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-13T16:57:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis is a great wee mod.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antgeth","CreatedById":96275,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-14T22:52:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Efantastic! been wishing for something of the sort since the time i planted my very first flag.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maltesh","CreatedById":17144,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-15T11:34:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHonestly, I probably should have thanked you for this a month back, so Thanks.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"civilwargeeky","CreatedById":69008,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-30T06:10:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust found this mod on CKAN and wanted to let you know that it is awesome \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commander Zoom","CreatedById":8333,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-30T06:28:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOh, thank you so much.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-30T13:24:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBrilliant!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbinDriveYards","CreatedById":137802,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-09T21:21:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHas anyone tested this on 1.0? Really hoping it still works...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xEvilReeperx","CreatedById":75857,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-10T12:31:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks for reminding me. The old version should still work but I recompiled anyway just in case\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbinDriveYards","CreatedById":137802,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-11T03:40:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks, that\u0027s great to hear! I run 50\u002B mods and this is one of my top 5 favorites for sure, thank you for keeping it up!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"iDisOrder","CreatedById":143952,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-09T18:53:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022xEvilReeperx\u0022 data-cite=\u0022xEvilReeperx\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThanks for reminding me. The old version should still work but I recompiled anyway just in case\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ewe need another update...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003Epuhleese!\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geschosskopf","CreatedById":69507,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-25T01:55:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpdate? Yes please \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xEvilReeperx","CreatedById":75857,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-25T02:27:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSure, looks like it didn\u0027t need any big changes. Updated\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Eskandare","CreatedById":62742,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-07T17:04:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to get a new download link?\u00A0\n\u00